title: Dragon.Age.Inquisition.The.Descent.DLC
description:
Install instructions:
1. Copy "__Installer" and "Update" folder to your Dragon Age: Inquisition directory 
2. Copy "ProfileOptions" file to your DA:I save directory C:Users{username}DocumentsBioWareDragon Age InquisitionSave
Note: This will enable you to unlock all currently released DLC as of 8/12/2015 if installed (including Red Lyrium weapons)
3. Overwrite
4. Play
PLEASE REMEMBER TO SEED, MANY OTHERS WANT THIS GAME! :)
